00:11:21.407 --> 00:11:22.616
zits dortn.

00:11:23.044 --> 00:11:25.232
zits dortn; me darf nit do. nu?

00:11:26.014 --> 00:11:28.100
ven ir flegt,

00:11:28.107 --> 00:11:31.643
fayern, purim, flegt ir z- geyn, f-

00:11:32.038 --> 00:11:33.348
farshtelt,

00:11:33.473 --> 00:11:34.867
in kostyumen?

00:11:33.726 --> 00:11:34.850
ikh nit.

00:11:35.194 --> 00:11:36.234
far vos?

00:11:36.223 --> 00:11:37.617
vayl ikh bin geven a kind.

00:11:37.607 --> 00:11:39.626
a kind geyt nisht farshtelt?

00:11:39.396 --> 00:11:44.689
m'iz gegangen, nor, denstmol nit, ⟨es iz⟩ geven nor di elte- di groyse mentshn flegn geyn purim.

00:11:44.695 --> 00:11:46.731
ikh fleg trogn shalakhmones.

00:11:46.720 --> 00:11:47.745
nu? ⟨⟩

00:11:47.293 --> 00:11:48.789
veyst vos s'heyst shalakhmones?

00:11:48.036 --> 00:11:51.962
yo. ir kent dertseyln, vos flegt ir ton tsu brengen shalakhmones?

00:11:51.715 --> 00:11:53.101
shalakhmones

00:11:53.101 --> 00:11:55.033
fleg ikh trogn tsu mayne fraynd.

00:11:55.765 --> 00:11:57.989
fleg ikh ⟨f- o-⟩ me fleg opbakn

00:11:57.989 --> 00:11:59.269
homen-tashn

00:11:59.443 --> 00:12:02.730
un fledlekh un, gute, tortn,

00:12:02.730 --> 00:12:07.452
un me fleg zikh f- di, eyn fraynd mitn andern flegn zikh baytn mit dem, shalakhmones.

00:12:08.826 --> 00:12:10.736
dos gedenk ikh fu- UNK.

00:12:10.736 --> 00:12:12.752
un me fleg mir gibn far yedn veg,

00:12:12.792 --> 00:12:14.567
fleg men mir batsoln.

00:12:15.390 --> 00:12:17.054
ir flegt betn gelt?

00:12:16.723 --> 00:12:17.623
neyn!

00:12:17.623 --> 00:12:19.046
zey flegn aleyn gibn.

00:12:19.508 --> 00:12:22.151
ir, ir flegt zingen lider far zey,

00:12:22.866 --> 00:12:24.294
oder epes azoy?

00:12:23.760 --> 00:12:25.391
ikh gedenk a bisl:

00:12:25.836 --> 00:12:30.352
"haynt iz purim un morgn iz oys. git mir a grosh, un shtup mikh aroys.

00:12:30.375 --> 00:12:35.499
git mir gikher, ikh darf di... kh'hob nit keyn tsayt. ikh darf avekgeyn tsun andere layt."

00:12:37.058 --> 00:12:40.609
dos, dos flegn mir zingen purim dortn.

00:12:41.277 --> 00:12:43.389
fleg geyn mit a grager, mit...

00:12:44.365 --> 00:12:47.329
i- ir flegt geyn in shul arayn hern di megile?

00:12:48.465 --> 00:12:51.412
⟨⟩, neyn. dos, mayn tate fleg geyn. ikh fleg nit geyn, neyn.

00:12:52.903 --> 00:12:55.845
 ver iz gegangen mit ayer tate davenen?

00:12:55.845 --> 00:12:59.091
nor er aleyn, tsi oykh andere, di kinder?

00:12:59.299 --> 00:13:01.470
fun di kinder zaynen,

00:13:02.640 --> 00:13:04.372
keyner iz nisht gegangen mit im?

00:13:04.648 --> 00:13:10.109
ikh gedenk? se fleg geyn, same di, di yinglekh flegn geyn. di meydlekh, ⟨n⟩eyn, flegn nit geyn in shil arayn.

00:13:12.782 --> 00:13:14.154
iz,

00:13:14.154 --> 00:13:17.585
 vos nokh gedenkt ir fun yidishe yontoyvim? ir gedenkt,

00:13:17.693 --> 00:13:19.509
 tsum bayshpil, khanike?

00:13:19.684 --> 00:13:22.091
vos hey-? yo, khanike gedenk ikh.

00:13:22.266 --> 00:13:24.791
khanike fleg ikh geyn in,...

00:13:26.721 --> 00:13:29.972
khanike gedenk ikh. ikh gedenk dos shvues.

00:13:30.383 --> 00:13:33.601
me fleg bakn,

00:13:33.910 --> 00:13:36.047
fun kez fleg men opbakn.

00:13:36.542 --> 00:13:38.578
ikh gedenk shvues, gedenk ikh.

00:13:39.175 --> 00:13:43.067
ikh gedenk simkhes-toyre fleg ikh geyn mit a royt fendl, mit an epl.

00:13:43.410 --> 00:13:46.779
di kleyne kinderlekh flegn geyn mit di fendelekh in,

00:13:48.439 --> 00:13:49.580
 mit, ⟨⟩...

00:13:48.574 --> 00:13:49.828
in shil arayn,

00:13:49.828 --> 00:13:50.829
oyf der nakht,

00:13:51.358 --> 00:13:53.160
tsu di hakofes.

00:13:52.742 --> 00:13:53.664
⟨,⟩ vos?

00:13:53.434 --> 00:13:55.335
hakofes, ⟨heyst⟩ mit der toyre.

00:13:55.864 --> 00:13:58.018
azoy fleg men zogn bay undz, "di hakofes."

00:13:59.678 --> 00:14:01.950
fun khanike gedenkt ir epes?

00:14:02.158 --> 00:14:04.852
ikh gedenk? khanike iz geven,

00:14:04.926 --> 00:14:08.109
akht teg. me fleg ontsindn ale tog a,

00:14:08.183 --> 00:14:09.527
a CA- a likhtl.

00:14:10.393 --> 00:14:15.129
un gelt darft, ir hot ge-, ir flegt bakumen gelt? khanike-gelt?

00:14:11.024 --> 00:14:12.024
UNK

00:14:15.321 --> 00:14:16.119
yo.

00:14:16.119 --> 00:14:19.568
me fleg gibn mir, ale kroyvim flegn kumen un gibn mir gelt.

00:14:20.839 --> 00:14:25.473
s'fleg kumen der onkl, der DYADYA, ver s'iz gevezn, der hot gegibn, khanike-gelt.

00:14:25.733 --> 00:14:29.237
un der pa-, der tate, der pape fleg mir gibn khanike-gelt.

00:14:29.361 --> 00:14:33.540
ale kinder. dos iz gevezn, az me f- darf oyf khanike gibn gelt.

00:14:34.963 --> 00:14:36.661
peysekh gedenkt ir?

00:14:36.579 --> 00:14:37.398
yo.

00:14:37.377 --> 00:14:39.639
vos, ir flegt,

00:14:39.908 --> 00:14:41.944
fregn di fir kashes,

00:14:42.928 --> 00:14:44.272
 peysekh?

00:14:43.114 --> 00:14:47.900
ikh hob nit gefregt di fir kashes, nor di, di eltere kinder hobn gefregt di fir kashes.

00:14:48.430 --> 00:14:50.972
yo, mayn tate fleg makhn dos,

00:14:51.484 --> 00:14:52.693
a seyder.

00:14:54.015 --> 00:14:55.765
er fleg zayn vi a meylekh.

00:14:55.765 --> 00:14:57.553
fleg zikh oysbetn a seyder.

00:14:57.627 --> 00:15:02.345
er fleg bahaltn dem, di matse ⟨afti- aftikoymen⟩... azoy hot er geheysn?

00:15:03.077 --> 00:15:04.505
AFIKOMAN, yo.

00:15:03.685 --> 00:15:05.231
afikoym- azoy?

00:15:04.967 --> 00:15:05.686
yo.

00:15:05.237 --> 00:15:06.058
yo?

00:15:06.064 --> 00:15:11.289
un ver s'ho- voser kind hot tsugeganvet, er fleg ⟨mit,⟩ fleg er darfn opgibn gelt un oyskoyfn.

00:15:11.802 --> 00:15:14.327
dos gedenk ikh., nu, es iz azoy,...

00:15:14.670 --> 00:15:18.157
un peysekh hobn mir gehat, tsveyerley pasudes:

00:15:18.855 --> 00:15:20.199
peysekhdike

00:15:20.458 --> 00:15:21.886
un khometsdike.

00:15:23.378 --> 00:15:26.645
un ir flegt aroyshelfn mitn baytn di teler?

00:15:26.854 --> 00:15:28.712
zog ikh aykh, iz dos geven,

00:15:28.712 --> 00:15:30.640
oyfn boydem hot men gehaltn teler

00:15:30.640 --> 00:15:33.935
mit di, vos oyf peysekh fleg men nor, in di esn.

00:15:36.338 --> 00:15:38.458
dos vos ikh gedenk fun peysekh.

00:15:39.915 --> 00:15:42.207
 volt ir gezogt, vi,

00:15:42.207 --> 00:15:45.430
vos iz geven ayer mishpokhe mit,

00:15:45.430 --> 00:15:47.857
vi iz geven mit gelt? ir hot gehat genug?

00:15:48.859 --> 00:15:50.709
ir volt, ir zayt geven

00:15:50.682 --> 00:15:51.502
neyn.

00:15:51.019 --> 00:15:53.156
raykh? tsi mitldik?

00:15:51.887 --> 00:15:53.699
neyn. mitl zenen mir geven.

00:15:53.699 --> 00:15:54.354
⟨ni- ge-⟩

00:15:54.563 --> 00:15:57.594
vos ⟨same a,⟩ a bal-melokhe vos kon zayn raykh?

00:15:58.630 --> 00:16:01.155
a mitl mentshn zenen mir geven; m'hot gelebt.

00:16:02.697 --> 00:16:04.480
ayer mame hot gearbet?

00:16:04.114 --> 00:16:05.120
neyn.

00:16:06.223 --> 00:16:10.267
iz geven demolt, a mark in shtot, in shtetl?

00:16:09.459 --> 00:16:10.878
yo. yo.

00:16:10.878 --> 00:16:12.032
s'iz geven a mark.

00:16:11.045 --> 00:16:12.816
iz vos gedenkt ir fun mark?

00:16:12.990 --> 00:16:14.097
ikh gedenk?

00:16:13.041 --> 00:16:16.396
ven, vi- vifl mol a, a khoydesh iz geven,

00:16:16.396 --> 00:16:18.168
oder vifl mol a vokh iz geven?

00:16:17.023 --> 00:16:18.184
ale tog.

00:16:18.168 --> 00:16:19.768
ale tog iz geven a mark?

00:16:19.071 --> 00:16:20.445
ale tog iz gevezn.

00:16:20.445 --> 00:16:26.326
azoy bay undz iz do di ⟨ts-⟩ di, frukhtn in droysn, azoy iz geven dortn; mentshn flegn shteyn un...

00:16:26.326 --> 00:16:27.800
geven ale tog a mark.

00:16:29.781 --> 00:16:33.015
un ayer tate oder mame zenen gegangen in mark

00:16:33.021 --> 00:16:34.351
koyfn oder

00:16:34.351 --> 00:16:35.546
farkoyfn?

00:16:35.907 --> 00:16:39.073
neyn! vos heyst ⟨zi fleg⟩ geyn, der tate fleg geyn koyfn?

00:16:42.100 --> 00:16:43.326
un

00:16:44.226 --> 00:16:47.578
vos zhe den hot men, ge- geesn? m'hot gedarft g⟨eyn⟩ koyfn epes!

00:16:47.668 --> 00:16:49.451
vos nokh gedenkt ir fun mark?

00:16:51.043 --> 00:16:53.450
vu iz geven der, der mark?

00:16:53.659 --> 00:16:55.070
fun alemen.

00:16:54.823 --> 00:16:59.891
NO, vu iz es geven in shtetl, in shtot? f- vu hot es zikh gefunen,

00:16:59.891 --> 00:17:00.791
der mark?

00:17:01.067 --> 00:17:02.580
nisht vayt fun aykh?

00:17:01.325 --> 00:17:02.433
⟨⟩

00:17:02.839 --> 00:17:04.470
ir gedenkt di gas?

00:17:07.260 --> 00:17:08.924
di gas gedenk ikh nit,

00:17:08.998 --> 00:17:13.683
nor ikh veys, s'iz geven a mark. es iz geven, esnvarg, aldings gevezn dortn,

00:17:14.297 --> 00:17:17.683
un e- dos iz geven, ot der mark iz geven mit esnvarg.

00:17:18.077 --> 00:17:23.133
un oyf tsu koyfn kleyder, dos iz geven di S- di magazinen, di STORES, ⟨u⟩n di...

00:17:23.477 --> 00:17:27.031
in mark zenen geven, mentshn mit,

00:17:27.814 --> 00:17:30.711
mit tishn, tsi mit, mit,...?

00:17:29.299 --> 00:17:30.811
yo. mit tishn.

00:17:31.375 --> 00:17:33.782
mit tishn. geshtanen mit tishn, avade.

00:17:34.193 --> 00:17:35.840
nit oyf der erd, ⟨⟩...

00:17:36.218 --> 00:17:37.393
nisht oyf der erd?

00:17:36.977 --> 00:17:38.591
neyn, oyf tishn.

00:17:38.476 --> 00:17:39.654
ale oyf tishn?

00:17:39.255 --> 00:17:40.194
YES.

00:17:40.521 --> 00:17:41.797
un,

00:17:41.922 --> 00:17:43.783
di poyerim flegn brengen,

00:17:43.783 --> 00:17:45.695
 khayes arayn?

00:17:43.795 --> 00:17:44.666
 yo.

00:17:45.499 --> 00:17:46.843
di poyerim? yo.

00:17:47.389 --> 00:17:51.804
di poyerim hobn gevoynt arum un arum di yidn. di yidn hobn gevoynt in shtot, un zey ⟨v-⟩...

00:17:51.810 --> 00:17:54.301
zey flegn arum un arum ⟨breng-⟩ aldings araynbrengen.

00:17:55.810 --> 00:17:58.774
un, vos far a loshn hot men gehert in mark?

00:17:59.185 --> 00:18:03.431
in mark hot men gehert yidish un, rumenish. yidish,

00:18:03.471 --> 00:18:05.119
meynsteyl yidish,

00:18:05.260 --> 00:18:06.452
vayl di,

00:18:07.302 --> 00:18:09.506
di vos zey hobn farkoyft iz geven a sakh yidn.

00:18:11.028 --> 00:18:14.299
s'iz geven rumener vos hobn geredt a bisl yidish oykh?

00:18:14.068 --> 00:18:14.939
neyn.

00:18:15.942 --> 00:18:18.023
di rumener hobn ⟨nit ge-⟩ nit geredt keyn...

00:18:18.023 --> 00:18:20.036
nu, s'iz geven a mol etlekhe,

00:18:20.042 --> 00:18:23.276
 vos zey flegn arbetn bay di yidn, flegn shoyn kenen yidish.

00:18:23.586 --> 00:18:24.744
tsi hot men

00:18:23.670 --> 00:18:24.929
di poyers.

00:18:25.515 --> 00:18:28.035
shabes-goyim, azelkhene zakhn?

00:18:28.497 --> 00:18:29.875
shabes-goyim?

00:18:30.555 --> 00:18:31.342
NO.

00:18:31.652 --> 00:18:33.806
s'iz geven bay aykh a shabes-goy?

00:18:35.010 --> 00:18:36.556
 s'iz geven in shil,

00:18:36.917 --> 00:18:40.761
vos er fleg kumen shabes, makhn fayer un di hrube heytsn.

00:18:40.761 --> 00:18:42.429
dos hot geheysn a shabes-goy.

00:18:43.093 --> 00:18:44.167
in shil.

00:18:45.000 --> 00:18:47.148
ontsindn shabes dortn,

00:18:47.148 --> 00:18:49.889
vos m'hot gedarft; nit der yid hot ongetsundn, nor

00:18:50.147 --> 00:18:51.474
der shabes-goy.

00:18:52.678 --> 00:18:54.190
ober in der heym nisht?

00:18:54.568 --> 00:18:57.161
in der heym iz nisht geven keyn shabes-goy bay aykh?

00:18:56.914 --> 00:18:57.785
neyn.

00:18:58.230 --> 00:19:02.864
nu, in der heym hot men nit ongetsundn gornit. me hot nit geheyt- m'hot gemakht fraytik yon-, shabes.

00:19:05.065 --> 00:19:06.341
iz,

00:19:07.292 --> 00:19:09.611
 tsigayner zaynen geven?

00:19:09.891 --> 00:19:12.703
nu, tsigayner, se flegn kumen eyn mol ⟨in⟩ yor.

00:19:14.093 --> 00:19:16.804
eyn mol in a yor? far vos? oder ven?

00:19:14.937 --> 00:19:15.979
yo.

00:19:15.979 --> 00:19:20.246
vayl zey v- zey fl- zitsn nit oyf eyn plats. me fleg zey nit lozn zitsn. zey flegn forn.

00:19:20.809 --> 00:19:27.468
flegn zey ale shtetlekh oysforn un, a mol flegn zey kumen tsun undz un zey flegn, zey flegn nit hobn keyn shtiber nit.

00:19:27.660 --> 00:19:29.274
zey hobn gevoynt in droysn.

00:19:30.023 --> 00:19:34.100
ir hot ⟨z-⟩ gehat tsu ton mit zey ven zey zaynen gekumen? hot zey gezen?

00:19:32.233 --> 00:19:33.138
NO.

00:19:34.292 --> 00:19:35.535
zey?

00:19:34.917 --> 00:19:35.738
YO.

00:19:35.535 --> 00:19:38.794
vos heyst nit gezen? mir hobn zey gezen; zey flegn geyn in shtot arayn.

00:19:38.794 --> 00:19:40.513
zey flegn kumen betn,

00:19:40.705 --> 00:19:44.816
me zol zey gibn dos,... azoy heyst es?... a, a nedove tsi vos.

00:19:45.970 --> 00:19:48.427
iz geven, yidishe betler oykh?

00:19:48.501 --> 00:19:49.558
s'iz geven.

00:19:49.716 --> 00:19:51.776
s'iz geven yidishe betlers oykhet.

00:19:52.180 --> 00:19:54.249
ve- vi oft flegn zey kumen?

00:19:55.150 --> 00:19:58.164
zey flegn kumen tsu ayer shtub betn gelt?

00:19:59.031 --> 00:20:01.084
nu, s'iz geven,

00:20:01.427 --> 00:20:03.314
me fleg,

00:20:03.314 --> 00:20:05.504
BOL'SHINSTVO flegn zey kumen ven?

00:20:06.355 --> 00:20:07.581
oyf yontev.

00:20:08.278 --> 00:20:12.035
oyf yontev, oyf purim flegn zey kumen. khanike

00:20:12.379 --> 00:20:16.440
flegn zey kumen, me zol zey... nu, s'iz geven etlekhe oreme-layt.

00:20:18.741 --> 00:20:20.051
iz,

00:20:23.685 --> 00:20:28.134
vos⟨e-⟩ vos nokh,... ir zayt geven frume yidn, volt ir gezogt?

00:20:27.634 --> 00:20:28.340
yo.

00:20:28.191 --> 00:20:31.577
iz geven a mikve? ir gedenkt, a mikve?

00:20:28.340 --> 00:20:28.978
yo.

00:20:30.250 --> 00:20:33.889
a mikve iz geven. vos heyst nit geven? s'iz geven a bod mit a mikve.

00:20:34.350 --> 00:20:35.525
s'iz geven.

00:20:37.303 --> 00:20:39.794
ir gedenkt dos? k- ir kent dos bashraybn?

00:20:41.556 --> 00:20:43.037
d- ikh kon bashraybn?

00:20:43.037 --> 00:20:44.691
ikh veys, s'iz geven a bod,

00:20:44.691 --> 00:20:48.587
un nokh dem iz geven a mikve vi a, gemakht azoy a,

00:20:51.208 --> 00:20:53.851
gemakht azoy a, vi a...

00:20:54.972 --> 00:20:56.833
un m'fleg aropgeyn oyf trep,

00:20:56.833 --> 00:20:59.774
tsvey-dray trepelekh fleg men aropgeyn. dos iz geven di mikve.

00:21:00.017 --> 00:21:01.530
un ir flegt geyn,

00:21:01.620 --> 00:21:04.111
 vi oft flegt ir geyn? mit der mame?

00:21:01.992 --> 00:21:06.323
mit der mamen⟨yu⟩. mit der mame flegn mir geyn, dos, fraytik.

00:21:12.910 --> 00:21:15.452
un, ir gedenkt khasenes?

00:21:15.306 --> 00:21:16.127
yo.

00:21:17.500 --> 00:21:19.570
vos heyst, ikh gedenk khasenes?

00:21:19.705 --> 00:21:24.946
vos f-, ir kent, dermonen far undz eyn khasene vos ir gedenkt, vi es volt oysgezen,

00:21:24.946 --> 00:21:26.116
vos hot pasirt?

00:21:27.827 --> 00:21:31.567
⟨, v-⟩ khasene, gedenk ikh⟨?⟩ me fleg shteln a khupe,

00:21:32.923 --> 00:21:35.347
un der rov fleg gibn khupe-kidushn.

00:21:37.934 --> 00:21:42.098
un a khasene fleg men makhn nor bay undz, shabes hot men nit gemakht,

00:21:43.136 --> 00:21:45.050
nor donershtik un montik.

00:21:46.544 --> 00:21:47.210
⟨v-⟩

00:21:48.550 --> 00:21:51.868
⟨v-⟩ ver hot khasene gehat fun ayer mishpokhe vos ir gedenkt?

00:21:54.169 --> 00:21:58.618
fun mishpokhe gedenk ikh nit. ikh gedenk di shkheynim hobn dortn khasene gemakht.

00:21:58.978 --> 00:22:00.372
dos gedenk ikh.

00:22:01.358 --> 00:22:04.406
v- vi lang hot men gefayert di khasene?

00:22:05.931 --> 00:22:07.370
 vi lang?

00:22:07.370 --> 00:22:10.734
a mol hot men gef- dray teg afile.

00:22:10.757 --> 00:22:13.923
eyn tog hot men oyfgerufn dem, dem khosn

00:22:14.250 --> 00:22:15.374
in shil.

00:22:15.938 --> 00:22:17.653
⟨un⟩ vos hot mit im geton?

00:22:20.713 --> 00:22:22.322
vos m'hot mit im geton?

00:22:22.322 --> 00:22:25.922
nu, hot men im oyfgerufn. er hot geda- m'hot gedavnt far im un er hot gedarft...

00:22:26.670 --> 00:22:29.651
d- dos, dos veys ikh, geven a oyfrufekhts.

00:22:29.843 --> 00:22:32.300
ikh veys, ir veyst vos dos heyst, tsi neyn?

00:22:32.053 --> 00:22:33.144
an oyfruf?

00:22:32.897 --> 00:22:33.802
yo.

00:22:33.345 --> 00:22:34.152
⟨yo⟩.

00:22:34.315 --> 00:22:36.789
an oyfruf, un nokh dem iz geven di khasene.

00:22:37.318 --> 00:22:40.585
der khosn iz geven bazunder un di kale iz geven bazunder.

00:22:41.841 --> 00:22:44.410
un nokh dem iz,...

00:22:43.782 --> 00:22:45.413
klezmer zaynen geven?

00:22:44.895 --> 00:22:45.665
yo!

00:22:45.739 --> 00:22:49.597
kle- ⟨a, m'iz,⟩ un nokh sheyne klezmer. yidishe klezmer, yidishe...

00:22:50.025 --> 00:22:52.364
s'iz geven a klezmer bay undz shtark sheyn.

00:22:55.155 --> 00:22:59.806
b-, bay, bay di, bay der khasene vos ir gedenkt, vifl klezmer zaynen gekumen?

00:23:00.353 --> 00:23:05.527
klezmer? s'iz geven epes a finef-zeks klezmers mit klarnetn un mit ⟨di⟩ fidlen un mit,...

00:23:06.124 --> 00:23:11.653
shtark sheyne m- muzik iz geven. yidishe muzik, ayngenemene muzik, azoy sheyne.

00:23:12.688 --> 00:23:16.614
ir gedenkt vos far a lider m'hot geshpilt? m'hot gezungen, tsi nor geshpilt,

00:23:16.958 --> 00:23:18.352
m'hot geshpilt.

00:23:17.194 --> 00:23:19.162
 melodyes?

00:23:18.763 --> 00:23:20.292
m- nor melodyes.

00:23:21.193 --> 00:23:22.714
m'hot geshpilt.

00:23:23.860 --> 00:23:26.503
iz, ir gedenkt,

00:23:27.488 --> 00:23:29.709
aza zakh vi kale baveynen?

00:23:29.563 --> 00:23:32.172
yo. "kalenyu, kalenyu veyn," DA.

00:23:32.500 --> 00:23:35.649
me fleg badek- badekn di kale, ⟨⟩, baveynen.

00:23:32.736 --> 00:23:33.641
ir ken-

00:23:34.558 --> 00:23:36.206
yo, badekn di kale.

00:23:36.212 --> 00:23:38.754
vo- vos zaynen di verter? ⟨ir⟩, ir kent dermonen?

00:23:38.457 --> 00:23:42.152
yo. ikh gedenk nit azoy; ikh bin geven a kind denstmol UNK.

00:23:41.764 --> 00:23:43.142
vos hot men geton?

00:23:47.147 --> 00:23:49.132
 ikh gedenk nit vos ⟨m'hot⟩ geton mit der kale.

00:23:51.113 --> 00:23:54.802
ah, m'hot zi ibergedekt mit der FATA. zi hot zikh gezetst oyf a b- m'hot zi...

00:23:57.855 --> 00:24:00.624
ikh gedenk dos, azoy me fleg shteln ⟨di⟩ khupe:

00:24:00.816 --> 00:24:02.801
der khosn fleg shteyn in mitn,

00:24:03.330 --> 00:24:05.283
un mir flegn zikh arumdreyen

00:24:05.283 --> 00:24:06.935
zibn mol arum, mir dakht.

00:24:07.515 --> 00:24:09.686
zibn mol hot men zikh arumgedreyt,

00:24:09.777 --> 00:24:12.184
un nokh dem hot er ongetun,

00:24:12.325 --> 00:24:13.466
der ring.

00:24:13.675 --> 00:24:15.255
dos iz geven di khasene.

00:24:17.421 --> 00:24:19.490
un dernokh vos hot pasirt?

00:24:21.235 --> 00:24:27.101
nu, nu, zey zenen gegan arayn ineveynik un me, me, m'iz ale arayn un m'hot geesn un m'hot getrunken.

00:24:27.377 --> 00:24:31.505
un, ⟨, un⟩ do, vi azoy iz b-, azoy iz a khasene?

00:24:29.065 --> 00:24:30.189
getantst?

00:24:32.575 --> 00:24:33.851
un,

00:24:34.026 --> 00:24:38.306
ment- mener un froyen hobn getantst tsuzamen tsi bazunder?

00:24:38.903 --> 00:24:40.129
ts- bazunder.

00:24:40.320 --> 00:24:42.474
mener bazunder un froyen bazunder.

00:24:43.999 --> 00:24:46.811
di froyen hobn gehat, zeyere eygene tantsn?

00:24:48.268 --> 00:24:52.700
di zelbe tants vos di mener; zey hobn getantst, a honge, a sher, a...

00:24:55.002 --> 00:24:57.176
 ir gedenkt az,

00:24:57.176 --> 00:25:00.261
tsi z- zaynen geven bad-, a badkhn

00:25:00.267 --> 00:25:01.830
bay der khasene?

00:25:01.318 --> 00:25:04.192
, ver zhe den hot gegibn khupe-kidushn?

00:25:06.898 --> 00:25:10.604
vos hot der badkhn geton? ir kent bashraybn a badkhn?

00:25:10.577 --> 00:25:11.786
der badkhn?

00:25:11.843 --> 00:25:14.216
ikh veys, er hot genemen a glezl vayn,

00:25:14.779 --> 00:25:16.781
un er hot gezogt di brokhes,

00:25:18.306 --> 00:25:20.850
un er hot gedavnt. dos gedenk ikh.

00:25:20.850 --> 00:25:22.957
nokh dem hot er gegibn trinken dem khosn,

00:25:23.588 --> 00:25:25.624
un der khosn hot gegibn der kale.

00:25:26.136 --> 00:25:28.391
 meyn gedenk ikh nit, vos,...

00:25:29.005 --> 00:25:31.091
vitsn hot er dertseylt oykh?

00:25:30.793 --> 00:25:31.715
?

00:25:31.367 --> 00:25:33.507
er hot ge- er hot gemakht vitsn

00:25:33.507 --> 00:25:34.669
farn oylem?

00:25:34.506 --> 00:25:35.360
yo.

00:25:36.447 --> 00:25:38.515
ir gedenkt,...?

00:25:39.400 --> 00:25:42.617
er fleg makhn vos, a opshpil di mekhutonim.

00:25:45.913 --> 00:25:49.788
yedn me- yedn balebos fleg er onrufn mitn nomen

00:25:50.183 --> 00:25:54.463
un makhn a mishebeyrekh... ⟨ir v- ir veyst vo- UNK az me makht⟩ a mishebeyrekh? ot azoy iz geven.

00:25:55.009 --> 00:25:55.914
yo?

00:25:57.355 --> 00:26:00.824
 ikh, vifl ikh gedenk dos, kon ⟨nor⟩ zogn.

00:26:04.493 --> 00:26:08.857
hot ir gehat, khaveyrimlekh vos zenen geven nisht-yidn?

00:26:09.235 --> 00:26:10.056
neyn.

00:26:10.779 --> 00:26:11.779
neyn.

00:26:12.289 --> 00:26:14.240
hot nisht gekent keyn nisht-yidn.

00:26:14.567 --> 00:26:17.070
vi hot ir zikh gelernt rumenish?

00:26:18.033 --> 00:26:18.746
in shul.

00:26:21.199 --> 00:26:26.824
in shul zenen geven yidn mit, mit goyim ts- tsuzamen?

00:26:24.068 --> 00:26:27.284
mit di, yo, yo, yo, tsuzamen.

00:26:28.671 --> 00:26:29.613
⟨SCUZĂ⟩.

00:26:29.586 --> 00:26:34.052
un di kinder flegn oyskumen gut, tsi zaynen geven gevise problemen

00:26:34.227 --> 00:26:35.453
tsvishn zey?

00:26:35.425 --> 00:26:39.474
a mol fleg zayn problemen, vi azoy ⟨VSYOZHKI⟩ ⟨iz dos⟩.

00:26:40.217 --> 00:26:44.795
s'iz, VOOBSHCHE geven problemen mit zey in eynem tsu lernen...

00:26:46.292 --> 00:26:48.935
 vos gede- gedenkt ir fun problemen

00:26:48.975 --> 00:26:50.656
tsvishn yidn un goyim

00:26:51.017 --> 00:26:52.057
fun di...?

00:26:51.051 --> 00:26:53.137
zey flegn undz onrufn mitn nomen.

00:26:53.751 --> 00:26:54.993
vos far a nemen?

00:26:56.282 --> 00:26:57.389
ZHID..

00:26:58.678 --> 00:27:03.785
az me fleg zikh a mol tsekrign tsi shlogn, in sh- in shul, azoy a kind, flegn zey...

00:27:05.091 --> 00:27:07.923
ir gedenkt a gevisn,

00:27:07.923 --> 00:27:09.591
a gevise tsayt ven

00:27:09.681 --> 00:27:12.695
ir hot zikh tsekrigt mit emetsn un

00:27:12.887 --> 00:27:15.024
m'hot aykh gerufn mit dem nomen?

00:27:14.710 --> 00:27:16.626
neyn. mikh nit.

00:27:18.169 --> 00:27:20.610
ayere brider un shvester hobn gehat problemen

00:27:22.506 --> 00:27:23.782
mit nit-yidn?

00:27:25.493 --> 00:27:26.394
neyn.

00:27:27.045 --> 00:27:27.818
hot,

00:27:27.818 --> 00:27:30.836
ayer tate oder mame zikh baklogn vegn,

00:27:31.332 --> 00:27:33.891
vegn, dem vos,

00:27:34.200 --> 00:27:36.286
mentshn hobn geshlogn yidn

00:27:36.411 --> 00:27:39.881
oder gemakht progromen? hot ir gehert fun pogromen?

00:27:38.976 --> 00:27:40.033
yo.

00:27:40.258 --> 00:27:41.636
vos hot ir gehert

00:27:42.148 --> 00:27:43.559
fun pogromen?

00:27:43.836 --> 00:27:47.188
ikh veys, mayn, mayn, tate fleg dertseyln

00:27:47.228 --> 00:27:49.871
az s'iz geven in Keshenev a pogrom oyf di yidn.

00:27:50.215 --> 00:27:51.964
m'hot,

00:27:52.864 --> 00:27:57.887
m'hot tsenemen di kleytn, m'hot barabevet di shtiber. dos iz geven der pogrom.

00:27:58.416 --> 00:28:02.865
hot men zeyer oft, dertseylt vegn dem Keshenever pogrom?

00:28:03.107 --> 00:28:04.842
zey hobn dertseylt, nor

00:28:04.842 --> 00:28:07.050
ikh kon gedenken? kh'bin geven a kind.

00:28:08.777 --> 00:28:10.492
ober iz geven,

00:28:12.186 --> 00:28:17.961
der progrom, iz bazundersh geven bakant tsvishn, mentshn in, in dem shtot?

00:28:15.848 --> 00:28:17.508
yo. yo.

00:28:19.088 --> 00:28:24.515
ir flegt, forn vu nit iz oyf vakatsyes zumertsayt?

00:28:24.589 --> 00:28:25.629
neyn.

00:28:24.825 --> 00:28:26.675
oder tsu kroyvim?

00:28:26.395 --> 00:28:30.405
neyn, bay Rumenye nit. UNK keyn mol nit aroysgeforn.

00:28:30.462 --> 00:28:33.223
ir zayt geblibn in sht- in shtot di gantse tsayt?

00:28:32.250 --> 00:28:33.725
shtetl di gantse tsayt.

00:28:34.292 --> 00:28:37.019
⟨, ⟩, itster veln mir iberbaytn di tashme,

00:28:37.093 --> 00:28:38.609
⟨kumen⟩ tsurik in a minutkele.
